â€œYes,â€ I said. â€œI felt it then. I only feel it in the evening. It was
rather bad that time.â€

Jack was silent a moment.

â€œFunny thing the door opening and shutting like that,â€ he said. â€œLetâ€™s
go indoors.â€

We got up and I remember seeing at that moment that the windows of my
