more, it is aggressive.â€

â€œBut â€˜itâ€™--what is â€˜itâ€™?â€ began the soldier, fuming. â€œWhat, in the name
of all thatâ€™s dreadful, _is_ a fire-elemental?â€

â€œI cannot give you at this moment,â€ replied Dr. Silence, turning to
